title: maDLC 2.2RC2 - cannot refine tracklets
body:
Hi,

I am using WIN10, GPU, DLC 2.2rc2. 

Ever since I upgraded from maDLC2.2b8 I cannot refine tracklets and I have tried using all the pickle files (ellipse, meta, full, assembly) generated during video analysis/convert to tracklets. 

I even created a new environment and did a clean install of maDLC 2.2rc2 and got an error about a missing CUDA file.

Thanks for all the hard work on DLC!
-Kyle
